## ============================================================
## Large model assets - NOT pushed to GitHub.
## GitHub rejects any single file > 100 MB and the model bundle
## is several GB. Distribute via Releases / HuggingFace / Drive.
## ============================================================
##
## Rule: ignore everything inside the model folders, then re-allow
## ONLY the small text/JSON config files needed at build time.

# ASR: ignore everything except config + vocab JSON
app/src/main/assets/asr/*
!app/src/main/assets/asr/config.json
!app/src/main/assets/asr/language_masks.json
!app/src/main/assets/asr/vocab.json

# Translation: ignore everything except the small dictionary JSON
# and the SentencePiece tokenizer model (~3 MB)
app/src/main/assets/trans/*
!app/src/main/assets/trans/dict.SRC.json
!app/src/main/assets/trans/dict.TGT.json
!app/src/main/assets/trans/tokenizer.model

# TTS: ignore each language's model.onnx (~114 MB each), keep tokens.txt
app/src/main/assets/tts/*/model.onnx

# Generic catch-all so any stray .onnx anywhere never sneaks in
*.onnx
